  "body": "When the batch submitter submits tx batches and state root batches, it might have the nonce error.\r\nThe problem is cause by running the two submitters at the same time, so both submitters might use the same nonce to submit the batches.\r\nhttps://github.com/ethereum-optimism/optimism/blob/85362d44fc13966f00bee26172dd04e6a442a6c6/packages/batch-submitter/src/exec/run-batch-submitter.ts#L457-L462",
